    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they had a cousin here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they sent him $5 to give it to me and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after one cousin sent a letter, we are trying so hard and everything, and now you're going to go to Israel?",
